{"id": 3500, "title": "Ticket #3500: Create Lark bridge, including moving routes and addresses", "description": "<blockquote>\nWhen we create the lark bridge, it will hose the system (networking-wise).  Why?\n<ul>\n<li>All the routes to the ethernet device are now invalid.\n</li><li>The IP address associated with the device should now be reassigned to the bridge.\n</li></ul>\n\n<p>We should copy over all the routes and addresses to the bridge itself.</p></blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2013-Feb-19 18:15</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=46460\">[46460]</a></span>: Handle case where device is already on bridge. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=3500\" title=\"Create Lark bridge, including moving routes and addresses\">#3500</a></span>  (By Brian Bockelman )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2013-Feb-19 18:06</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=46459\">[46459]</a></span>: Move IPv4/IPv6 addresses to bridge interface. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=3500\" title=\"Create Lark bridge, including moving routes and addresses\">#3500</a></span>  (By Brian Bockelman )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2013-Feb-19 17:13</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=46458\">[46458]</a></span>: Working version of rou